      "chinese": "原住民的部落幾乎都有從原鄉遷移的經驗。牽動族人移地、移住的最根本原因，是為了擴大部落領域；遠離外族侵犯；或是為了獵場、迷信、水源、瘟疫、天災造成土地的破損流失；也有被統治者強行遷村，尤其是日本時期及民國時期。",
      "ab": "sana acekele ki kacalrisilrisiya, yadrepele ka makitwa talela twalai ki nataikaikaiyanelini. kudra ngualailringalini si talelaela, amani kai apaswadrava ku taikaiya tucekele, akidaila ki badha, talupa, lrisi, taciladha, sualrubu, langualai ki tasulisiya ki takisedreka si ngilisianenga ku daedae, yakai lukipatalela ki wahavase liniya ka sihu, inilringa saamani kai Dripungu si kaciyukuka.",
